oads-ssl.webflow.com/6196411cd4f2104fcc8f6e05/6196bc5c21cb1a93f21570fc_03_graphgl.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="service-icn"><div class="service-bg product"></div><div class="service-bg pink"></div></div><div role="listitem" class="service-item w-dyn-item"><div class="service-top"><h4 class="service-heading">Stepfunctions</h4><p class="service-paragraph">Low-code, visual workflow for distributed applications. </p></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6196411cd4f2104fcc8f6e05/6196c43b6e036a60dd1b9986_04_stepfunctions.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="service-icn"><div class="service-bg product"></div><div class="service-bg pink"></div></div><div role="listitem" class="service-item w-dyn-item"><div class="service-top"><h4 class="service-heading">IAM</h4><p class="service-paragraph">Fine-grained Identity and Access Mangement across all AWS.</p></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6196411cd4f2104fcc8f6e05/6196c46dd2e01f43a2c69c2e_05_IAM.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="service-icn"><div class="service-bg product"></div><div class="service-bg pink"></div></div><div role="listitem" class="service-item w-dyn-item"><div class="service-top"><h4 class="service-heading">EventBridge</h4><p class="service-paragraph">Serverless, event-driven applications at scale.</p></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/6196411cd4f2104fcc8f6e05/6196c483ab885f807383bbbb_06_eventbridge.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="service-icn"><div class="service-bg product"></div><div class="service-bg pink"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="approach" data-w-id="617be1d3-8edc-a9b0-8313-1798e1b38dd7" class="hww wf-section"><div class="hww-con"><div class="hww-text-con"><div class="hww-text-top"><h1 class="heading-2">How we work</h1></div><div class="hww-text-lower"><div class="hww-dots"><div class="hww-dot"></div><div class="hww-dot"></div><div class="hww-dot"></div><div class="hww-dot"></div><div class="hww-dot"></div></div><div class="hww-text-block" style="will-change: transform; transform: translate3d(0px, 0vh, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d;"><div class="block first"><h2 class="heading-4">Identify the problem</h2><p class="hww-paragraph">We’ll talk about your products, ideas and create a space for us to understand your goals and for you to spar with us about the problems you’re trying to solve. From this foundation we will present suggestions on how we can be of service to bring your ideas to life.</p></div><div class="block"><h2 class="heading-4">Define the process</h2><p class="hww-paragraph">Every project is different and so should the process be. We’ll define a clear framework of how we communicate, exchange feedback and effectively work together. We believe openness, honesty and trust goes a long way.</p></div><div class="block"><h2 class="heading-4">Kickoff</h2><p class="hww-paragraph">Once we are ready to get going, we will choose a start date and kick off the onboarding process. We will work closely with you to arrange how we move forward, defining the resources &nbsp;needed to accelerate the process.</p></div><div class="block"><h2 class="heading-4">Collaborate</h2><p class="hww-paragraph collaborate">We are very honest and open. But we expect to hear from you what things are working and how we can improve our process together. Taking things as early in the process as possible is crucial.</p></div><div class="block"><h2 class="heading-4">Iterate</h2><p class="hww-paragraph">We are firm believers in delivering small but very valuable pieces of work as quickly as possible. We want the product in the hand of your users so we can get real-world feedback, learn and improve without stalling the development process.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="hww-graphics-con"><div class="number-con"><div class="number-block" style="will-change: transform; transform: translate3d(0px, 0%, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) 